@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<section class="privacy-policy fade-in delay-1">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>Your privacy is important to me. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information collected on this site and how it is used.</p>

    <h2>1. Information Collected</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact Information</strong>: If you choose to contact me through a form or email link, your name and email address may be collected.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Basic analytics (e.g., Google Analytics) may collect anonymized data about how visitors interact with the site, such as pages visited, time spent, and browser/device type.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How Your Information Is Used</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Responding to inquiries</li>
        <li>Improving the website and user experience</li>
        <li>Understanding general traffic patterns and site performance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This site may use third-party services such as:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> for tracking website usage</li>
        <li><strong>Email service providers</strong> for handling contact form submissions</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These third-party services have their own privacy policies and do not receive access to any personally sensitive information from this site.</p>

    <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
    <p>Cookies may be used to improve user experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer not to allow them.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>Reasonable steps are taken to protect any personal information submitted via this site, but no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

    @* <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>If you have contacted me and would like your personal data removed from my records, please send a request via email.</p> *@

    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
</section>
